I feel more at ease.

31
00:07:12,560 --> 00:07:14,160
I still want to work with you.

32
00:07:19,750 --> 00:07:20,830
Wake up soon,

33
00:07:23,430 --> 00:07:25,560
we're all waiting for you to come back.

34
00:07:45,270 --> 00:07:46,470
The Leader Group case

35
00:07:47,070 --> 00:07:48,510
has been handed over to the department

36
00:07:48,510 --> 00:07:50,040
for special case handling.

37
00:07:50,560 --> 00:07:52,360
Division Three can close the case for now.

38
00:07:52,360 --> 00:07:53,960
During this investigation,

39
00:07:54,270 --> 00:07:56,130
the comrades from Division Three

40
00:07:56,270 --> 00:07:57,600
were brave, tenacious,

41
00:07:58,040 --> 00:07:59,370
fearless of sacrifice,

42
00:07:59,720 --> 00:08:00,720
patient, steady,

43
00:08:00,870 --> 00:08:01,800
and determined.

44
00:08:02,000 --> 00:08:02,730
Thank you all

45
00:08:03,720 --> 00:08:06,270
for your selfless contributions and sacrifices

46
00:08:06,270 --> 00:08:08,730
in solving the Leader Group espionage case.

47
00:08:10,560 --> 00:08:13,020
After discussions with senior leadership,

