00:08:18,360 --> 00:08:19,750
and Tian Ziwei are awarded

51
00:08:19,750 --> 00:08:21,680
second-class individual merits.

52
00:08:45,960 --> 00:08:47,480
Keep up the good work

53
00:08:48,080 --> 00:08:49,270
and keep moving forward.

54
00:08:49,270 --> 00:08:50,240
Defend the land,

55
00:08:50,790 --> 00:08:51,990
and fulfill your duty

56
00:08:52,150 --> 00:08:54,510
to protect the people and the country.

57
00:08:55,720 --> 00:08:57,250
Everyone in Division Three

58
00:08:58,200 --> 00:08:59,660
has done an excellent job.

59
00:08:59,910 --> 00:09:00,370
Salute!

60
00:09:26,720 --> 00:09:27,270
Tian.

61
00:09:30,480 --> 00:09:31,030
Nurse.

62
00:09:32,550 --> 00:09:33,270
Where...

63
00:09:33,870 --> 00:09:35,000
Where's Tian Ziwei?

64
00:09:35,240 --> 00:09:37,170
She might have gone for a check-up.

65
00:09:37,630 --> 00:09:38,490
Thanks though.

66
00:09:42,120 --> 00:09:43,150
Well.

67
00:09:44,550 --> 00:09:45,550
I came here to thank you,

68
00:09:45,550 --> 00:09:46,680
but you're not here.

69
00:09:47,150 --> 00:09:48,670
What's that supposed to mean?

70
00:09:48,670 --> 00:09:50,730
You don't want to hear me talk, do you?

71
00:09:51,240 --> 00:09:52,510
Let me tell you.

72
00:09:54,080 --> 00:09:55,440
That day with Luca,

73
00:09:56,670 --> 00:09:58,070
we both sank into the sea.

74
00:09:58,150 --> 00:09:58,960
We were both suffocating.

75
00:09:58,960 --> 00:10:00,090
I just kept sinking,

76
00:10:00,120 --> 00:10:01,240
but then I suddenly thought of you.

77
00:10:01,240 --> 00:10:02,360
I thought about you

78
00:10:02,510 --> 00:10:03,960
falling into the sea.

79
00:10:04,630 --> 00:10:05,630
I was so worried.

80
00:10:06,910 --> 00:10:08,170
I immediately woke up.

81
00:10:08,480 --> 00:10:09,910
And I started swimming up.

82
00:10:09,910 --> 00:10:11,870
I have no idea where the strength came from,

83
00:10:11,870 --> 00:10:13,840
but I made it to the surface.

84
00:10:14,790 --> 00:10:15,650
It was amazing.

85
00:10:16,960 --> 00:10:18,560
I never thought I could do it.

86
00:10:21,790 --> 00:10:22,670
Actually,

87
00:10:24,320 --> 00:10:26,150
I didn't just come to thank you.

88
00:10:29,910 --> 00:10:32,370
During the time you've been in the hospital,

89
00:10:32,600 --> 00:10:34,750
I felt like the whole world went quiet.

90
00:10:35,840 --> 00:10:36,790
I didn't enjoy it

91
00:10:37,150 --> 00:10:39,080
at all.

92
00:10:39,720 --> 00:10:41,380
It even makes me a bit anxious.

93
00:10:43,120 --> 00:10:44,200
Back then,

94
00:10:44,200 --> 00:10:46,860
why did I always joke about
you talking too much?

95
00:10:49,000 --> 00:10:51,800
But honestly, your voice is actually really nice.

96
00:10:52,200 --> 00:10:53,460
I like listening to it.

97
00:10:55,550 --> 00:10:56,080
I like it.

98
00:10:58,320 --> 00:10:59,720
Just the voice?

99
00:11:05,120 --> 00:11:06,250
When did you come in?

100
00:11:08,000 --> 00:11:09,930
I didn't even hear your footsteps.

101
00:11:11,910 --> 00:11:14,240
I think your voice sounds really nice now.

102
00:11:15,480 --> 00:11:16,280
Keep talking.

103
00:11:22,870 --> 00:11:24,270
What's with the silence?

104
00:11:24,750 --> 00:11:26,750
You were talking non-stop earlier.

105
00:11:26,870 --> 00:11:27,790
Keep going.

106
00:11:28,720 --> 00:11:30,180
Do you only like the voice?

107
00:11:30,870 --> 00:11:32,070
What else do you like?

108
00:11:50,840 --> 00:11:51,970
Comrade Tian Ziwei.

109
00:11:52,120 --> 00:11:53,630
This is the second-class medal of honor

110
00:11:53,630 --> 00:11:55,290
awarded to you by the country.

111
00:11:57,550 --> 00:11:58,610
Thank you, leader.

112
00:12:04,550 --> 00:12:06,750
Anyway, you heard everything earlier.

113
00:12:08,390 --> 00:12:09,720
I just want to tell you,

114
00:12:11,240 --> 00:12:12,550
you're my medal.

115
00:12:14,790 --> 00:12:15,520
Is that okay?

116
00:12:16,750 --> 00:12:17,680
What do you mean?

117
00:12:18,600 --> 00:12:19,750
I like you.

118
00:12:20,910 --> 00:12:21,750
Is that okay?

119
00:12:23,630 --> 00:12:24,890
Give me a clear answer.

120
00:12:30,150 --> 00:12:31,390
Why are you so fierce

121
00:12:31,390 --> 00:12:32,920
when you confess your love?

122
00:12:38,390 --> 00:12:38,850
I get it.

123
00:12:40,030 --> 00:12:41,760
But honestly, I kind of like it.

124
00:12:46,320 --> 00:12:46,550
Ah.

125
00:12:55,630 --> 00:12:57,430
Why didn't you say that earlier?

126
00:12:58,120 --> 00:12:59,780
You're quite good with words.

127
00:13:00,550 --> 00:13:01,720
Say it again.

128
00:13:02,600 --> 00:13:03,840
I won't say it again.

129
00:13:03,840 --> 00:13:05,970
I'll only say it once in this lifetime.

130
00:13:45,670 --> 00:13:46,630
Zhao Yaning.

131
00:14:06,600 --> 00:14:07,080
Behind you.

132
00:14:07,080 --> 00:14:07,870
Careful!

133
00:14:09,840 --> 00:14:10,910
You're awake.

134
00:14:12,390 --> 00:14:13,510
You can't move yet.

135
00:14:13,630 --> 00:14:14,960
Let me help you lie down.

136
00:14:26,030 --> 00:14:27,360
How did I end up here?

137
00:14:27,720 --> 00:14:28,510
You were unconscious.

138
00:14:28,510 --> 00:14:29,970
Someone brought you here.

139
00:14:36,720 --> 00:14:38,120
How long have I been unconscious?

140
00:14:38,120 --> 00:14:39,050
It's been 3 days.

141
00:14:42,320 --> 00:14:43,440
Who brought me here?

142
00:14:43,440 --> 00:14:44,440
A woman.

143
00:14:44,510 --> 00:14:45,480
Her name's Zhao Yaning.

144
00:14:45,480 --> 00:14:46,510
She was injured too.

145
00:14:46,510 --> 00:14:47,770
She's in the next room.

146
00:14:52,750 --> 00:14:54,320
Sir, you can't pull it out.

147
00:14:54,480 --> 00:14:55,790
You're not fully recovered yet.

148
00:14:55,790 --> 00:14:56,390
Sir.

149
00:14:59,240 --> 00:15:00,360
You can't run, Sir.

150
00:15:07,670 --> 00:15:08,480
You're awake.

151
00:15:13,550 --> 00:15:14,360
Where is she?

152
00:15:18,910 --> 00:15:19,630
She's gone.

153
00:15:23,510 --> 00:15:24,320
How could

154
00:15:24,320 --> 00:15:25,780
a person be gone like that?

155
00:15:27,510 --> 00:15:29,110
It's not that kind of 'gone'.

156
00:15:35,390 --> 00:15:36,630
Where is she now?

157
00:15:37,390 --> 00:15:38,850
You've been out for 3 days.

158
00:15:41,550 --> 00:15:43,080
Let's go outside for a walk.

159
00:15:45,200 --> 00:15:45,800
I'm sorry.

160
00:15:46,720 --> 00:15:48,320
I kept this from you for a bit.

161
00:15:49,480 --> 00:15:52,000
It's time for you to know everything now.

162
00:15:53,270 --> 00:15:55,670
Everything Zhao Yaning said was true.

163
00:15:57,080 --> 00:15:58,000
She's one of us.

164
00:15:58,870 --> 00:16:01,000
She's from the Chinese Ministry of State Security.

165
00:16:01,000 --> 00:16:02,930
A member of the Jiangshan Project.

166
00:16:03,480 --> 00:16:04,340
Her codename is

167
00:16:04,960 --> 00:16:06,120
Jiangshan 2047.

168
00:16:07,150 --> 00:16:08,480
The Jiangshan Project?

169
00:16:09,030 --> 00:16:09,760
What's that?

170
00:16:11,630 --> 00:16:12,440
It's a talent development program

171
00:16:12,440 --> 00:16:13,910
designed to protect

172
00:16:15,120 --> 00:16:17,320
our country's interests and security.

173
00:16:18,000 --> 00:16:19,730
Only a few people know about it.

174
00:16:20,000 --> 00:16:21,460
Zhao Yaning's superior is

175
00:16:21,630 --> 00:16:22,430
Chairman Xie,

176
00:16:23,270 --> 00:16:24,080
Xie Rujun?

177
00:16:24,550 --> 00:16:25,000
Yes.

178
00:16:25,840 --> 00:16:26,960
Many years ago,

179
00:16:27,440 --> 00:16:28,390
when Chairman Xie was still working

180
00:16:28,390 --> 00:16:30,510
in Chinese Ministry of State Security,

181
00:16:30,510 --> 00:16:31,570
he already foresaw

182
00:16:31,840 --> 00:16:32,840
that future China

183
00:16:33,080 --> 00:16:34,880
would have greater development

184
00:16:35,440 --> 00:16:38,670
and would also face more severe international situations.

185
00:16:38,670 --> 00:16:40,120
It was necessary to prepare in advance

186
00:16:40,120 --> 00:16:41,450
to meet the challenges.

187
00:16:41,750 --> 00:16:42,360
So,

188
00:16:42,960 --> 00:16:43,820
on the surface,

189
00:16:43,870 --> 00:16:45,130
Chairman Xie resigned

190
00:16:45,360 --> 00:16:46,960
from the Chinese Ministry of State Security.

191
00:16:46,960 --> 00:16:47,820
But in reality,

192
00:16:48,240 --> 00:16:50,030
he used his position as the president of

193
00:16:50,030 --> 00:16:52,270
the Jiangcheng International Trade Association as a cover,

194
00:16:52,270 --> 00:16:54,670
while continuing to handle top-secret missions.

195
00:16:54,670 --> 00:16:56,530
He would select qualified people

196
00:16:56,720 --> 00:16:58,360
from the State Security,

197
00:16:59,320 --> 00:17:01,000
train them rigorously,

198
00:17:01,440 --> 00:17:04,680
and send them to the frontlines
of intelligence operations

199
00:17:04,680 --> 00:17:06,609
to protect the nation's security.

200
00:17:06,829 --> 00:17:07,550
That was

201
00:17:08,109 --> 00:17:09,440
the Jiangshan Project,

202
00:17:09,920 --> 00:17:13,310
a program to nurture talents of State Security.

203
00:17:17,640 --> 00:17:18,270
Back then,

204
00:17:18,880 --> 00:17:21,790
Zhao Yaning was chosen by Chairman Xie

205
00:17:22,349 --> 00:17:24,240
because of her exceptional language skills

206
00:17:24,240 --> 00:17:25,829
and excellent adaptability.

207
00:17:25,829 --> 00:17:28,510
Chairman Xie is her superior.

208
00:17:29,070 --> 00:17:31,400
But isn't Chairman Xie still in a deep coma

209
00:17:32,150 --> 00:17:33,550
in Jiangcheng Hospital?

210
00:17:33,920 --> 00:17:35,250
That was a long time ago.

211
00:17:37,110 --> 00:17:38,240
He woke up?

212
00:17:39,310 --> 00:17:40,510
Yes, half a month ago.

213
00:17:41,440 --> 00:17:42,680
He contacted me,

214
00:17:43,310 --> 00:17:44,480
and that's when

215
00:17:45,310 --> 00:17:46,910
I knew about Jiangshan 2047.

216
00:17:47,440 --> 00:17:48,500
I also learned that

217
00:17:49,110 --> 00:17:50,510
Zhao Yaning was one of us,

218
00:17:51,070 --> 00:17:53,330
She specializes in long-line missions.

219
00:17:55,310 --> 00:17:56,680
But for your safety,

220
00:17:57,070 --> 00:17:59,160
it was best to maintain the current situation.

221
00:17:59,160 --> 00:18:00,290
So I didn't tell you.

222
00:18:01,070 --> 00:18:02,510
At that time,

223
00:18:03,350 --> 00:18:05,610
we decided you'd continue with the case.

224
00:18:05,720 --> 00:18:06,750
Jiangshan 2047

225
00:18:07,350 --> 00:18:09,010
would remain by James's side.

226
00:18:10,070 --> 00:18:12,310
I would only tell you when necessary.

227
00:18:13,440 --> 00:18:15,160
To sacrifice you short-term undercover agent

228
00:18:15,160 --> 00:18:18,480
to protect the long-term one.

229
00:18:21,200 --> 00:18:22,000
I understand.

230
00:18:24,440 --> 00:18:26,170
So nothing like that happened,

231
00:18:27,070 --> 00:18:28,800
which is why you didn't tell me.

232
00:18:29,350 --> 00:18:29,880
Exactly.

233
00:18:30,880 --> 00:18:32,810
You had already started your work.

234
00:18:33,920 --> 00:18:34,720
Fortunately,

235
00:18:35,160 --> 00:18:36,420
at the crucial moment,

236
00:18:36,640 --> 00:18:37,840
she stepped forward.

237
00:18:50,440 --> 00:18:51,440
Where is she now?

238
00:18:55,720 --> 00:18:57,380
That's highly confidential.

239
00:18:58,200 --> 00:18:59,130
I can't tell you.

240
00:19:22,030 --> 00:19:22,830
Come in.

241
00:19:29,590 --> 00:19:31,720
Mr. Xie, long time no see.

242
00:19:33,030 --> 00:19:34,430
It hasn't been that long.

243
00:19:35,270 --> 00:19:36,680
Jiangshan 2047,

244
00:19:37,310 --> 00:19:38,440
you've worked hard.

245
00:19:40,110 --> 00:19:42,270
It's thanks to our last meeting

246
00:19:42,590 --> 00:19:45,650
that a lot of things
went much more smoothly afterward.

247
00:20:13,350 --> 00:20:19,030
The private room is ready.
Dinner's prepared.

248
00:20:40,160 --> 00:20:41,020
Please come in.

249
00:20:47,310 --> 00:20:48,200
Mr. Xie.

250
00:20:53,270 --> 00:20:54,530
You're finally awake.

251
00:20:57,110 --> 00:20:58,240
You've worked hard.

252
00:20:59,240 --> 00:21:01,200
After you woke up and contacted me,

253
00:21:01,750 --> 00:21:05,030
I learned that Yang Guang
and the others would also be coming to Lianhai.

254
00:21:05,030 --> 00:21:07,430
That kept me from being alone in this fight.

255
00:21:07,440 --> 00:21:10,100
This operation's success is also thanks to you.

256
00:21:31,310 --> 00:21:32,240
Lady.

257
00:21:33,880 --> 00:21:36,110
Who are you looking for?

258
00:21:36,750 --> 00:21:38,960
Are you sure everything's okay?

259
00:21:39,590 --> 00:21:40,990
Yes, everything's fine.

260
00:21:56,270 --> 00:21:57,790
It's been hard on you.

261
00:21:58,830 --> 00:22:00,830
I know that you've done a lot

262
00:22:01,160 --> 00:22:03,020
since you arrived in Jiangcheng.

263
00:22:20,440 --> 00:22:21,240
I've arrived.

264
00:22:21,480 --> 00:22:22,610
Everything is fine.

265
00:22:23,070 --> 00:22:24,310
It's been arranged.

266
00:22:26,640 --> 00:22:28,310
Tomorrow, 9 AM.

267
00:22:28,640 --> 00:22:29,240
Okay.

268
00:22:29,790 --> 00:22:30,440
Remember.

269
00:22:31,070 --> 00:22:32,790
No matter the outcome,

270
00:22:33,240 --> 00:22:34,110
report it to me.

271
00:22:35,310 --> 00:22:37,830
Also, keep a close eye on them.

272
00:22:39,000 --> 00:22:40,660
They're up to take something.

273
00:22:40,920 --> 00:22:44,070
Handle any problem once they come up.

274
00:22:45,310 --> 00:22:46,590
I'll take care of it.

275
00:22:59,750 --> 00:23:00,810
When we talk later,

276
00:23:01,000 --> 00:23:02,270
make sure you all

277
00:23:02,400 --> 00:23:03,920
write it down as much as you can.

278
00:23:03,920 --> 00:23:06,030
Including the key points in his words.

279
00:23:06,030 --> 00:23:07,760
It's best if you can make notes.

280
00:23:16,830 --> 00:23:19,920
Hello, the number you've dialed is currently…

281
00:23:27,750 --> 00:23:30,510
I've arrived, you can contact me.

282
00:23:49,240 --> 00:23:52,240
Two hours after the meeting. Jiangcheng Park.

283
00:24:04,030 --> 00:24:05,920
The time I went to Jiangcheng to see you,

284
00:24:05,920 --> 00:24:07,200
I was there to report

285
00:24:07,440 --> 00:24:09,480
the intel on Leader's plan to

286
00:24:09,480 --> 00:24:11,540
act on the Gen-4 nuclear energy tech.

287
00:24:11,960 --> 00:24:14,690
I didn't expect you to suddenly have an accident.

288
00:24:55,720 --> 00:24:57,650
At that time, I was really worried.

289
00:24:58,830 --> 00:25:00,690
